# CVE-2026-33671 — picomatch vendored inside next/dist/compiled/picomatch
#
# This copy of picomatch is bundled directly into the Next.js distribution and
# cannot be upgraded independently via pnpm. We have already upgraded Next.js
# to the latest available release (16.2.3). This finding will be resolved
# automatically when Next.js ships an updated compiled bundle.
CVE-2026-33671
